div.div: A normal high school boy Kisaragi Ryuji's peaceful life is turned into an adventure by the return of his second cousin Eriko. Ryuji and Eriko seize a relic box from a black broker. In the box, they find a red dragon girl Rose. In order to protect Rose from the black organization, Ryuji decides to fight using his power as a relic handler.

This is the story of an orphan, L Shu. He is not any regular orphan, but a metahuman experiencing the changes in himself, his country and the world during the dawn of the magical era. Watch as L Shu embarks on a journey to hone his peculiar abilities together with his sister, the adorable and charismatic L Xiaoyu. Along the way, theyll encounter supernatural events, obstacles and even the most powerful people in their country. How will L Shu make the best of his abilities and oust his never-ending list of rivals and opponents?
(Source: Webnovel)
